==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Far-off
<hw>Far"-off`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Remote;
<as>as, the <ex>far-off</ex> distance; troops landing on
<ex>far-off</ex> shores</as>. Cf. <cref>Far-off</cref>, under
<er>Far</er>, adv.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> faraway.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>remote in time; <as>as, <ex>far-off</ex> happier
times</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> remote, removed.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>far-out</ent>⟦br⟧
